ssets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ("},{"pid":"dfc7f452eddb04d0d4cdb3088e07dc978b389e89","tid":697702,"uid":102240,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:43:57.000Z","msg":"可能你真係覺得梁天埼抵坐監，但好值得考慮係咪要坐六年<br />\n<br />\n我都好憎港獨，但大是大非唔係一味仇恨，咩鍵完國要清算波台係班傻仔既幻想，我地唔駛清算人，希望大家停止抽水，留黎插班等食人血饅頭既「獨派」好過"},{"pid":"7eee4907a1c7c4750586832cadefc05b51904bf0","tid":697702,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:44:55.000Z","msg":"襲警判一年合理<br />\n暴動判五年就真係幾重手下"},{"pid":"16440bd567cedda7a003e8f26759f60333dd7281","tid":697702,"uid":2169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"今日連咩咩妹都食左藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1758a0f0c5088ebb08cd6993508b72f20b90bd0d","tid":697702,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:45:53.000Z","msg":"岩呀，天琦6年好慘<br />\n7年果個唔知乜水就算啦，坐多兩碌都ok"},{"pid":"6c6968173d6e8f397e5917ad6464964cbf4db84b","tid":697702,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce771714a7b2e031b705b94b5aad12f16420f3fd","tid":697702,"uid":2436,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:46:14.000Z","msg":"蔣狗講人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我覺得港獨派一直以來嘅活動雷聲大雨點少<br />\n尤其是係連登嘅活躍分子 一直黨同伐異 又唔嘗試去令其他人信服 其他人有質疑就比人話係五毛<br />\n拖低晒成個港獨派嘅形象 其他人想加入都俾人趕走啦"},{"pid":"b789548bc1b4ed0f12c640ea0c0a1f0e255c9bf1","tid":697702,"uid":102240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7eee4907a1c7c4750586832cadefc05b51904bf0","tid":697702,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:44:55.000Z","msg":"襲警判一年合理<br />\n暴動判五年就真係幾重手下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"跟返大隊2-3碌咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo